{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe44688440","title":"谢富治谈谭震林问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"90cb761291","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":14,"articleId":"fe44688440","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"谭震林","id":"89f0012853","type":"人物"},{"name":"谢富治","id":"93cca4665d","type":"人物"},{"name":"各级党政领导人","id":"a59dfa2519","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cb1f363c04","type":"title","text":"谢富治谈谭震林问题","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e0d2b5922","type":"paragraph","text":"〖1967年5月14日下午两点，在市革委会全体委员会议前就农林口问题请示了谢副总理〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d0a9b6b41","type":"paragraph","text":"问：现在外面传说，毛主席在一次会上说过：有人不是要打倒谭震林？他今天还参加会来了！毛主席真这样说过吗？","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33308daa2a","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：没有这么回事，我参加会议没有听见主席这么说过，这是有人造谣！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f5864b961","type":"paragraph","text":"问：今后农林口的问题怎么搞？谭震林的问题怎么搞？","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cce5dcb8fa","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：你们自己干嘛！继续深入地批判他！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85efcc8240","type":"paragraph","text":"说：谭震林五月一日上天安门后，农林口形势有很大变化，他的秘书吕伊波五月二日突然死去了，有恐怖气氛！","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b809accdef","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：吕伊波揭发了谭震林吗？","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"35691b50ae","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他写了一个揭发谭震林问题的提纲，还来不及揭发，就突然死去了，死的原因我们正在调查。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c0f485021a","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：不论过去、现在，或者将来，你们批判谭震林的错误都是对的。即使将来给他工作，你们批判他也是对的。保守派要保就是错的。你们可以把这些问题反映给总理。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe44688440","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}